Subject: NEA Attribute Changes Report Error
Description:
Not sure if this broke or never worked on our end, but when I attempt to run "Attribute Changes" report in NEA GUI, it says "No Records Found".

The management would want this fixed soon. See screenshot from NEA GUI.
Solution_Comment__c:
Issue:
Checking the report for an object under attributeChange shows no information.

Cause:
The object and time frame we were looking at does not have any events to display, leading to a blank display.

Resolution:
No change was needed, we verified that changes were coming in and that these changes were showing in the appropriate objects.
